**Changed by:** PR #1089 -- consolidate 17 batch/mass PR operation skills into 3
**Verification:** verified-ci

### What changed
- Added Round 5 deduplication result: batch/mass/parallel-pr-* cluster (17->3, 82% reduction)
- Added 1 new Failed Attempts row: single monolithic skill for heterogeneous clusters
- Updated Outcome summary to reflect 5 rounds total
- Updated "Top Duplicate Clusters Remaining" note with PR #1089 resolution
