### Why
The batch/mass PR operations cluster (17 files: batch-pr-*, mass-pr-*, parallel-pr-*, bulk-pr-*, pr-ci-*)
was the next large deduplication target. Split into 3 skills by operational scenario (CI fixing, conflict
rebasing, worktree isolation) rather than merging all 17 into one monolith — validates the sub-grouping
pattern when a cluster covers distinct triggering scenarios.

